description: A base repostitory implementation to be used in message-drive, CQRS-based architectures
summary: A base repostitory implementation to be used in message-drive, CQRS-based architectures. Caters for event sourced solutions, but allows for entity-based solutions as well. This is an opinionated framework, in the manner that it forces all changes to entities to happen through events (even in entity-based solutions), which are optionally published to a bus. Moreover, reconstitution loigic for ES solutions that applies the events is decoupled from any aggregates\state and happens in a stateless, functioal-language-like manner.

The object model is very similar to what proposes System.Xml, but for HTML documents (or streams).
